                    "text": "Until the next time it acts, the zaramuun appears to be a sand dune. It has an automatic result of 47 (50 in sandy terrain) on <a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Deception</a> and <a aonid=\"15\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Stealth</a> checks and DCs to pass as a sand dune. Any creature that walks onto the zaramuun moves into its body and is Engulfed.",
