                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "<b>Requirements</b> The zaramuun hit with a melee Strike with its last action, or it has a creature Engulfed. <b>Effect</b> The zaramuun attempts to Disarm one primarily metal or stone object from the Struck or Engulfed creature and casts its innate dimensional anchor on the target creature.",
