                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "text": "The zaramuun can <a aonid=\"93\" game-obj=\"Actions\">Burrow</a> through sand and dirt (but not stone) at its full burrow Speed, leaving no tunnel or sign of its passing. Any Engulfed creatures are left behind when it Burrows. Loose sand and scree are not difficult terrain for a zaramuun.",
