                    "text": "The zaramuun sprays a blast of sand that deals 11d10 slashing damage to all creatures in a 60-foot line (Reflex DC 38). It can\u2019t Sandblast again for 1d4 rounds. <br/><b>Critical Success</b> No effect.<br/><b>Success</b> Half damage.<br/><b>Failure</b> Full damage.<br/><b>Critical Failure</b> Full damage and blinded for 1 round.",
